110505 | title=Kieran MacDonald leaves after a season | publisher=[[BBC Sport]] | work=bbc.co.uk/sport | date=31 August 2015 | accessdate=2 September 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Daniel Armstrong (footballer)|Daniel Armstrong]]\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.|Wolverhampton Wanderers]]\n| [[Free transfer (football)|Free]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.expressandstar.com/sport/football/wolverhampton-wanderers-fc/2015/10/27/wolves-sign-youngster-daniel-armstrong/ |title=Wolves sign youngster Daniel Armstrong |work=Express & Star |publisher=MNA Media |date=27 October 2015 |accessdate=10 February 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|group=\"nb\"}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Hamilton Academical F.C. seasons}}\n{{2015\u201316 in Scottish football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2015-16 Hamilton Academical F.C. Season}}\n[[Category:Hamilton Academical F.C. seasons|2015-16]]\n[[Category:Scottish football clubs 2015\u201316 season|Hamilton Academical]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toMichael McGovern(link changed toMichael McGovern (footballer); link changed toMichael McGovern (footballer); link changed toMichael McGovern (footballer)) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2015%E2%80%9316_Hamilton_Academical_F.C._season"}
