fc.co.uk/|publisher=Motherwell FC|accessdate=23 September 2015|date=23 September 2015}}</ref>\n\nOn 13 October 2015, [[Mark McGhee]] returned to the club as manager.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34511651 |title=Motherwell name Mark McGhee as manager for second spell |work=BBC Sport |publisher=BBC |date=13 October 2015 |accessdate=13 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Mark McGhee returns as Motherwell boss|url=http://www.motherwellfc.co.uk/2015/10/13/mark-mcghee-returns-as-motherwell-boss/|website=www.motherwellfc.co.uk|publisher=Motherwell F.C.|accessdate=13 October 2015|date=13 October 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Results & Fixtures==\n{{legend2|#ccffcc|Win|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#ffffcc|Draw|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#ffcccc|Loss|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#cccccc|Postponed|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n\n===Pre-season Friendlies===\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 7 July 2015\n|time = 18:00 [[British Summer Time|BST]] ([[UTC+01:00|UTC+1]])\n|round = \n|team1 = Motherwell \n|score= 1-1\n|report = [http://www.motherwellfc.co.uk/2015/07/07/borussia-ii-1-1-motherwell/ Report]\n|team2 = [[Borussia M\u00f6nchengladbach II|Borussia M\u00f6nchengladbach U-23]]\n|goals1 = [[Wes Fletcher|Fletcher]] {{goal|49}}\n|goals2 = [[Giuseppe Pisano|Pisano]] {{goal|70}}\n|stadium = VV Rheden\n|location = [[Rheden]], [[Netherlands]]\n|attendance = \n|referee = \n|result = D\n|stack= yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 9 July 2015\n|time = 18:00 [[British Summer Time|BST]] ([[UTC+01:00|UTC+1]])\n|round = \n|team1 = Motherwell \n|score= 0-0\n|report = [http://www.motherwellfc.co.uk/2015/07/09/sc-heerenveen-0-0-motherwell/ Report]\n|team2 =  [[SC Heerenveen|Heerenveen]]\n|goals1 = \n|goals2 = \n|stadium = Sportvereniging Langezwaag\n|location = [[Drachten]], [[Netherlands]]\n|attendance = \n|referee = \n|result = D\n|stack= yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 14 July 2015\n|time = 14:00 [[British Summer Time