2920538.aspx|website=www.readingfc.co.uk|publisher=Reading F.C.|accessdate=25 January 2016|date=25 January 2016}}</ref>\n| MF\n| {{flagicon|WAL}}<ref group=N>Taylor was born in [[Ascot, Berkshire|Ascot]], [[England]], and but chose to represent Wales, qualifying through his grandfather who has born in [[Barry Island|Barry]]. Taylor has represented Wales at [[Wales national under-17 football team|U-17]], [[Wales national under-19 football team|U-19]], [[Wales national under-21 football team|U-21]] and [[Wales national football team|Senior]] level.</ref>\n| [[Jake Taylor (footballer)|Jake Taylor]]\n| [[Reading F.C.|Reading]]\n|-\n| 1 September 2015<ref>{{cite web|title=Man Utd\u2019s Grimshaw joins on loan|url=http://www.motherwellfc.co.uk/2015/09/01/man-utds-grimshaw-joins-on-loan/|website=motherwellfc.co.uk/|publisher=Motherwell F.C.|accessdate=2 September 2015|date=1 September 2015}}</ref>\n| 11 January 2015<ref>{{cite web|title=Grimshaw returns south|url=http://www.motherwellfc.co.uk/2016/01/12/grimshaw-returns-south/|website=www.motherwellfc.co.uk|publisher=Motherwell F.C.|accessdate=12 January 2016|date=12 January 2016}}</ref>\n| MF\n| {{flagicon|ENG}}\n| [[Liam Grimshaw]]\n| [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n|-\n| 1 February 2016<ref>{{cite web|title=Gomis makes Motherwell move|url=http://www.motherwellfc.co.uk/?p=50044|website=motherwellfc.co.uk/|publisher=Motherwell F.C.|accessdate=1 February 2016|date=1 February 2016}}</ref>\n| End of season\n| MF\n| {{flagicon|SEN}}\n| [[Morgaro Gomis]]\n| [[Heart of Midlothian F.C.|Heart of Midlothian]]\n|-\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Loans out===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"  style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%; \"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:200px;\"| Date from\n! style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:200px;\"| Date to\n! style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:45px;\"| Position\n! style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:45px;\"| Nationality\n! style=\"background: