 January 2016}}</ref>\n| End of season\n| FW\n| {{flagicon|SCO}}\n| [[David Clarkson]]\n| [[St Mirren F.C.|St Mirren]]\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Released===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"  style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%; \"\n|-\n!  style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:150px;\"| Date\n!  style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:55px;\"| Position\n!  style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:55px;\"| Nationality\n!  style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:200px;\"| Name\n!  style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:200px;\"| Joined\n!  style=\"background:#ffa000; color:98285c; width:150px;\"| Date\n|-\n| 26 January 2016<ref>{{cite web|title=Goalkeeper Dan Twardzik departs|url=http://www.motherwellfc.co.uk/2016/01/26/goalkeeper-dan-twardzik-departs/|website=www.motherwellfc.co.uk|publisher=Motherwell F.C.|accessdate=26 January 2016|date=26 January 2016}}</ref>\n| GK \n| {{flagicon|GER}}\n| [[Dan Twardzik]]\n| [[VSG Altglienicke]]\n| 2018\n|-\n| 31 May 2016<ref name=\"Players Released\">{{cite web|title=Squad Update: May 2016|url=http://www.motherwellfc.co.uk/2016/05/16/squad-update-may-2016/|website=motherwellfc.co.uk|publisher=Motherwell F.C.|accessdate=19 May 2016|date=16 May 2016}}</ref>\n| GK \n| {{flagicon|SCO}}\n| Brett Long\n| \n| \n|-\n| 31 May 2016<ref name=\"Players Released\"/>\n| MF\n| {{flagicon|SCO}}\n| [[Jack Leitch]]\n| [[Airdrieonians F.C.|Airdrieonians]]\n| 2 September 2016<ref>{{cite web |url=http://spfl.co.uk/news/article/leitch-joins-airdrieonians/ |title=Leitch joins Airdrieonians |work= |publisher=SPFL |date=2 September 2016 |accessdate=3 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 31 May 2016<ref name=\"Players Released\"/>\n| FW\n| {{flagicon|SCO}}\n| [[David Clarkson]]\n| [[St Mirren F.C.|St Mirren]]\n| 1 June 2016<ref>{{cite web|title=Clarkson staying with St Mirren|url=http://spfl.co.uk/news/article/clarkson-staying-with-st-mirren/|website=spfl.co.uk|publisher=SPFL|accessdate=3 June 2016|date=19 May 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n