y Law]] || Motherwell ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| FW || [[Niall McGinn]] || [[Aberdeen F.C.|Aberdeen]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| FW || [[Michael Higdon]] || Motherwell ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| FW || [[Leigh Griffiths]] || [[Hibernian F.C.|Hibernian]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n|}\n\n====First Division====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Pos.!!Player!!Club!!Appearance\n|-\n| GK ||  style=\"width:200px;\"| [[Scott Fox]] || style=\"width:200px;\"| [[Partick Thistle F.C.|Partick Thistle]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Stephen O'Donnell (Scottish footballer born 1992)|Stephen O'Donnell]] || Partick Thistle ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Jordan McMillan]] || Partick Thistle ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Callum Morris]] || [[Dunfermline Athletic F.C.|Dunfermline Athletic]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|- style=\"background:#ffff44;\"\n| DF || [[Aaron Taylor-Sinclair]] {{double-dagger}} || Partick Thistle ||align=\"center\"|2\n|-\n| MF || [[Stefan Scougall]] || [[Livingston F.C.|Livingston]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| MF || [[Michael Tidser]] || [[Greenock Morton F.C.|Greenock Morton]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| MF || [[Stuart Bannigan]] || Partick Thistle ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| FW || [[Brian Graham (footballer)|Brian Graham]] || [[Raith Rovers F.C.|Raith Rovers]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| FW || [[Lyle Taylor]] || [[Falkirk F.C.|Falkirk]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| FW || [[Chris Erskine]] || Partick Thistle ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n|}\n\n====Second Division====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Pos.!!Player!!Club!!Appearance\n|-\n| GK ||  style=\"width:200px;\"| [[Lee Robinson (footballer)|Lee Robinson]] || style=\"width:200px;\"| [[Queen of the South F.C.|Queen of the South]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Chris Mitchell (Scottish footballer)|Chris Mitchell]] || Queen of the South ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Mark Durnan]] || Queen of the South ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Ben Gordon (footballer, born 1985)|Ben Gordon]] || [[Alloa Athl