0030 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=18 April 2014 |date=18 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Falkirk and Rangers dominate team of the year voting |first= |last= |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27080275 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=18 April 2014 |date=18 April 2014}}</ref>\n\n====Premiership====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Pos.!!Player!!Club!!Appearance\n|-\n| GK ||  style=\"width:200px;\"|[[Fraser Forster]] || style=\"width:200px;\"| [[Celtic F.C.|Celtic]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Graeme Shinnie]] || [[Inverness Caledonian Thistle F.C.|Inverness Caledonian Thistle]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Virgil van Dijk]] || Celtic ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Mark Reynolds (footballer)|Mark Reynolds]] || [[Aberdeen F.C.|Aberdeen]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Andrew Robertson (footballer)|Andrew Robertson]] || [[Dundee United F.C.|Dundee United]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| MF || [[Stuart Armstrong]] || Dundee United ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| MF || [[Peter Pawlett]] || Aberdeen ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| MF || [[Kris Commons]] || Celtic ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| FW || [[Stevie May]] || [[St Johnstone F.C.|St Johnstone]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-style=\"background:#33ff99;\"\n| FW || [[Kris Boyd]] {{dagger}} || [[Kilmarnock F.C.|Kilmarnock]] ||align=\"center\"|3\n|-\n| FW || [[Nadir Ciftci]] || Dundee United ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n|}\n\n====Championship====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Pos.!!Player!!Club!!Appearance\n|- style=\"background:#ffff44;\"\n| GK ||  style=\"width:200px;\"| [[Michael McGovern]] {{double-dagger}} || style=\"width:200px;\"| [[Falkirk F.C.|Falkirk]] ||align=\"center\"|2\n|-\n| DF || [[Paul McGinn]] || [[Dumbarton F.C.|Dumbarton]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Will Vaulks]] || Falkirk ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Stephen Kingsley]] || Falkirk ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| DF || [[Ziggy Gordon]] || [[Hamilton Academical F.C.|Hamilton Academical]] ||align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| MF ||